Come Fly With Me

Written in: C++

This work was a culmination of multiple experiments of interesting algorithms I found.

Built in Unity using C++, I used perlin noise to create landscapes that are traversed over by a plane. The plane itself is controlled using motion capture via a Kinect V2. There are also multiple other AI controlled planes traversing the landscape using various flocking algorithms.
